Package event

Provides the classes necessary to create and manage events in the simulation.

This package includes:

  • AntMoveEvent - an event where an ant moves to the next node in the graph.
  • Event - an abstract class representing an event in the simulation.
  • EventInterface - an interface for events in the simulation.
  • EventManager - a singleton class that manages and handles events in the simulation.
  • PheromoneEvaporationEvent - a pheromone evaporation event in the simulation.
  • PrintEvent - an event that prints the status of the simulation.
